data.description: Beautiful, well maintained home in Cherokee Hills. Only minutes from down town Knox or Sevierville. Quiet, Country setting. Recently updated, this lovely home features new LVP flooring, recent paint and updates. New kitchen appliances. Large expanded and enclosed rear porch area, and new deck with installed grill. The large fenced back yard offers privacy and pastoral setting. Available for showing 11/17 OPEN HOUSE 11/19 2-4PM
